<HTML> 
<HEAD>
<TITLE> The Esperantist Movement's humanitarian activities in the two World Wars and its relationship with the International Red Cross</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>

<P>
<P>
<P>
<TABLE>
<TR valign=top><TD>
<P><IMG SRC="/gifsICRC/IconICRC.gif" ALIGN=left HSPACE=10></TD><TD>
