<HTML> 
<HEAD>
<TITLE> Argentina: Declaration in accordance with Article 90  of Protocol I </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>

<P>
<P>
<P>
<TABLE>
<TR valign=top><TD>
<P><IMG SRC="/gifsICRC/IconICRC.gif" ALIGN=left HSPACE=10></TD><TD>
