	<BR>
*	DURAND, Andr&eacute;, <I>History of the International Committee of the Red Cross</I>, Vol. II: <I>From Sarajevo to Hiroshima</I>, Henry Dunant Institute, Geneva, 1984, 675 pages.<BR>
	<BR>
