<P>
<H2>The Kingdom of Swaziland and the Additional Protocols of 1977</H2>
<P><I></I>
<P>
<P><B><I>Corrigendum</I></B><BR>

<P>Contrary to the announcement in No. 309 of the <I>Review</I>, November-December 1995, p. 678, the Kingdom of Swaziland became party to the two Protocols by <B>accession </B>(and not by ratification).<BR>

