<P><B>International Review of the Red Cross</B>  <B>no 308, p.576</B><BR>
</TD></TR></TABLE>

<P><IMG SRC="/gifsICRC/Separator_Line_ICRC.gif" BORDER=0><BR>

<P>
<P>
<H2>Accession of the Federated States of Micronesia to the Geneva Conventions and their Additional Protocols</H2>
<P><I></I>
<P>
<P>On 19 September 1995, the Federated States of Micronesia acceded to the four Geneva Conventions of 12 August 1949 and to their Additional Protocols of 8 June 1977.<BR>

<P>These instruments will come into force for the Federated States of Micronesia on 19 March 1996.<BR>

<P>The Federated States of Micronesia is the <B>186th </B>State party to the Geneva Conventions. It is the <B>140th </B>State party to Protocol I and the <B>131st </B>State party to Protocol II.<BR>

<P>
